import React from 'react'
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom'
import './index.css'
import App from './App'
import { BrowserRouter } from 'react-router-dom'
ReactDOM.render( <React.StrictMode>
    <BrowserRouter> <App />
    </BrowserRouter> </React.StrictMode>, document.getElementById('root')
)
